description: We are purchasing the MLS Supporters' Shield so all Major League Soccer fans can own a piece of the regular season trophy!
payDisclosure: Shield DAO token holders can have their funds redeemed if the Supporters Shield is not purchased. If successful, total funding amount will be used to purchase the Shield as well as make a significant donation to the charity of the Supporters' Shield Foundation's choice.
